      },
      {
        "text": "Overall, these results are consistent with snRNA-seq analysis, and confirm largely non-overlapping expression of Ebf1 and Htr4 within Drd1 cells (Fig",
        "id": "4_1_9"
      },
      {
        "text": "We previously demonstrated that a single acute cocaine exposure differentially alters the transcriptome of molecularly defined cell types within the NAc (Savell et al., 2020)",
