        "id": "2_1_24"
      },
      {
        "text": "The integration of over 39,000 nuclei from rats that underwent different cocaine exposure paradigms identified two populations of Drd1-expressing MSNs (Drd1-MSN-1 and Drd1-MSN-2; Fig",
        "id": "3_1_1"
      },
      {
        "text": "To begin understanding the distinct gene expression signatures of these Drd1-MSN populations, we conducted a differential expression analysis using pseudobulked gene expression matrices",
        "id": "3_1_3"
